title: Take Me Home: The John Denver Story (2000)
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0224214/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0224214/</a>

Heartwarming story of the well-known singer who died tragically all too young, with many of his original soundtracks. I think Chad Lowe (brother of Robert) makes a good effort in portraying John Denver, but many of the hard-boiled fans have vented their rage on Imdb, as usual.

Good stereo sound, fullscreen (made for TV). Burn tested, runs well in my divX player
